■ We have implemented a Brain Computer Interface (BCI) for image reconstruction based on Rapid Serial Visual Presentations (RSPVs) of polygons, that act as primitives for images.
■ A Linear Discriminant Analysis (LDA) classifier was trained to discriminate brain activity and retrieve correct pieces from given pictures.
■ Subjects had a high success probability when reconstructing a set of given pictures.
